Output scaffold.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "Fira Code"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 0.06s



Type "npx --yes @antardev/forge-dev@latest  scaffold my-custom-preset"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Type "npx --yes @antardev/forge-dev@latest init my-custom-preset my-app"
Enter
Sleep 6s
